"1  garlic clove, minced","1/4 cup fresh lime juice","2 tablespoons fish sauce","1 tablespoon dark brown sugar","2  small fresh red Thai chiles, thinly sliced, or 1 serrano pepper, seeded and minced","6 cups torn romaine lettuce","1/2  seedless cucumber, halved lengthwise and thinly sliced","2  medium shallots, thinly sliced into rings","1/2 cup roughly torn fresh mint, divided","1/3 cup roughly torn fresh cilantro, divided","8 ounces thickly sliced rare deli roast beef, cut into wide strips","1/3 cup coarsely chopped dry-roasted peanuts"